org.apache.flex.abc.semantics

Class Instruction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.abc.semantics.Instruction
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArbitraryOperandsInstruction, ImmediateOperandInstruction, NoOperandsInstruction, OneOperandInstruction

    public abstract class Instruction
extends Object
    A representation of an ABC instruction. Note that an instance of Instruction may be shared or reused.
